    <refsect1 xml:id="description"><title>Description</title>
        <para>
            <function>cross</function> returns the cross product of two
            vectors, <parameter>x</parameter> and <parameter>y</parameter>,
            i.e.
                $\begin{pmatrix}
                    { x[1] \times y[2] - y[1] \times x[2] } \\
                    { x[2] \times y[0] - y[2] \times x[0] } \\
                    { x[0] \times y[1] - y[0] \times x[1] }
                 \end{pmatrix}$.
        </para>
    </refsect1>
